snippet.title: Buckle up! Hello Engineer comes out this summer.
snippet.description:
Unleash your inner designer https://www.helloengineer.com/

We know you've been eagerly awaiting the opportunity to transform questionable scrap into functional works of art. 🎨 Well, the wait is almost over! Prepare to embark on an adventure in a mysterious amusement park, scavenging and crafting to overcome mind-bending challenges. Let your creativity soar this summer!

Learn more about Hello Engineer:
https://www.helloengineer.com/

Want to party up with other inventors? Join the Neighbor Games Discord server! 
http://discord.gg/NeighborGames

Follow us on social media:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/NeighborGamesHQ
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/NeighborGamesHQ
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/NeighborGamesHQ
Tiktok: https://www.tiktok.com/@tinybuild?lang=en
